prompts.frontCover: A charming and humorous watercolor illustration of a cute, cartoonish sloth wearing a party hat, hanging upside down from a tree branch and struggling adorably to reach a delicious-looking birthday cake that is just out of its grasp on the ground below. The sloth has a look of comical determination. The scene is painted with soft, flowing watercolor washes, with visible artistic brush strokes and organic paint bleeds on a textured paper background. In the center, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, the text reads: "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao! Let's get wild... slowly."
